title: Ep. 171 "Good Girl Gone Bad" ft. Esonica Veira of Temptation Island Season 2
description: What happens when a good girl goes bad?  Were we ever really good?  Join us this week as we chat with Esonica Veira of Temptation Island Season 2 about good girls going bad, and so much more than just what you saw on TV.
